âœ… Check interface status	show ip interface brief	Router / Switch	Verify interface status and IPs
âœ… Check interface details	show interfaces	Router / Switch	Check bandwidth, errors, and status
âœ… Trace path to host	tracert [destination IP]	PC	View hops taken to reach a host
